    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>lentils </strong>and <strong>tomato stock</strong> to the pan and reduce the heat to low – this is your <strong>lentil mixture</strong></p><p>Return the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> to a low heat with a splash of<strong> milk</strong> and a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Mash until smooth and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong></p>",
