    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pour the <strong>lentil mixture</strong> into the base of an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>, then spread the <strong>mash </strong>evenly on top and grate over the <strong>lighter</strong> <strong>cheese</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until golden and bubbling – this is your <strong>veggie shepherd’s pie</strong></p><p>While your pie is cooking, wash, then rip the leaves off the <strong>spring greens</strong>, discard the tough stalks, then layer the leaves over each other, roll them up and slice into thin strips</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
