    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate large, wide-based pan with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>and the <strong>sliced spring greens </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 4 min or until the spring greens are cooked with a slight bite – these are your <strong>garlicky greens</strong></p>",
