    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, remove the <strong>veggie shepherd's pie</strong> from the oven and leave to stand for a few min as it will be extremely hot! (this will also help the flavours develop)</p><p>Serve the <strong>veggie shepherd's pie</strong> with the <strong>garlicky greens </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
